      <li>Trace the execution of unnested conditionals and conditionals inside loops.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Challenges: 15 min
    <ul>
      <li>Trace the execution of this conditional statement.</li>
      <li>Fill in the blanks so that this function replaces negative values with zeroes.</li>
      <li>Modify this program so that it only processes files with fewer than 50 records.</li>
      <li>Modify this program so that it always finds the largest and smallest values in a list
no matter what the list‚Äôs values are.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

